skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: barefoot church
des: Listen to the latest sermons from Barefoot Church. You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done for the day. You can also ask for the previous or next sermon by saying "Alexa, previous" or Alexa, next".
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
